# Gap Map Linking

- Treat Gap Map as the problem catalog, not the tool ontology.
- Compute tool-to-gap links on this side of the system.
- Public rankings must expose score breakdowns and assumptions.
- Record what missing evidence blocks confidence.
- Avoid black-box applicability scores.
